children.description: Given I go to the self test page
NavigateTo /self-test.html

children.source: Given I go to the self test page

children.description: Then I can see 'Hello Self Test page'
WaitForPageTitle "Hello Self Test page"
And if I click the 'click me' button
ClickSubmitButton "click me"

children.source: And if I click the '<btn_text>' button

children.description: Then I can see "Wahoo" message
FindById show-text-on-button-click-text-div-id and text = "Wahoo"
And I dont see "number one option" in select id select_id
AssertSelect id="select_id" text="number one option" is not currently selected
children.source: AssertSelect id="<select_id>" text="<option_value>" is not currently selected
And I dont see "<option_value>" in select id <select_id>

children.description: And I see "number two option" in select id select_id
AssertSelect id="select_id" text="number two option" is currently selected
children.source: AssertSelect id="<select_id>" text="<option_value>" is currently selected
And I see "<option_value>" in select id <select_id>

children.description: Then I choose "number three option" in select id select_id
ChooseOption "number three option" in id select_id

children.source: Then I choose "<option_value>" in select id <select_id>

children.description: And I see "number three option" in select id select_id
AssertSelect id="select_id" text="number three option" is currently selected
children.source: AssertSelect id="<select_id>" text="<option_value>" is currently selected
And I see "<option_value>" in select id <select_id>

ClickById click-id

children.source: And if I click the Click by id button

FindById show-text-on-id-click-text-div-id and text = "Wahoo Two"

children.source: Then I can see another "<msg>" message

children.description: And if I click the 'delayed click' button

children.source: And if I click the '<btn_text>' button

FindByIdTimeout show-text-on-deplayed-id-click-text-div-id timeout = 10 secs

children.source: Then I see "<msg>" after a pause

children.description: Given I enter "some text" into the text field
FindByTagAndAttributes tag="?input"? attributes=\[name="named_text_field",maxlength="10",size="10"\]
ClearAndSendKeys "some text"

children.source: Given I enter "<txt>" into the text field

children.description: Then the text field will contain "some text"
FindByName "?named_text_field"?
AssertCurrentElement attribute="value" value="some text"

children.source: Then the text field will contain "<txt>"

children.description: And the field located beneath the heading has the text 'some child text'
FindById parent_div_id
FindChild ByTagAndAttributes tag="?span"? attributes=\[class="some_class"\]
AssertCurrentElement text="some child text"

children.source: And the field located beneath the heading has the text '<txt>'

children.description: And I can click the link "a text link" and see "clicked a link"
ClickLink "a text link"
FindById show-text-on-link-click-text-div-id
AssertCurrentElement text="clicked a link"

children.source: And I can click the link "<link_text>" and see "<txt>"

children.description: Given radio button with text "radio - option 1" is checked

children.description: Given radio button with text "radio - option 2" is not checked
